{"title":"01: Attention is all you need","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"01: Attention is all you need","author":"Yuyang Zhang","reading_time":5},"headingText":"Preliminary","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\nFor a demonstration of a line plot on a polar axis\n\n![image-20250701223807429](01-attention.assets/image-20250701223807429.png)\n\n\n### Dot Product Similarity（点积相似度）\n\n给定两个向量 $\\mathbf{q}, \\mathbf{k} \\in \\mathbb{R}^d$\n\n它们的点积为:\n\n$$\n\\text{score} = \\mathbf{q} \\cdot \\mathbf{k} = \\sum_{i=1}^{d} q_i k_i\n$$ {#eq-dot-product}\n\n- 测量两个向量的**相似度**, 数值越大，说明两个向量越相似\n- 在 Self-Attention 中，用来衡量“当前词对其他词的关注程度”\n\n### Softmax 函数\n\n给定向量 $\\mathbf{x} = (x_1, x_2, \\ldots, x_n)$，Softmax 函数定义为:\n$$\n\\text{Softmax}(x_i) = \\frac{e^{x_i}}{\\sum_j e^{x_j}}\n$$ {#eq-softmax}\n\n\n- 将注意力“得分（dot product）”转换为概率分布\n- 每个词对其他词的注意力权重 $\\alpha_{ij} \\in [0, 1]$\n\n![The Transformer Family Version 2.0 | Lil'Log](01-attention.assets/transformer.png)\n\nThis is the figure see, figure @eq-softmax","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\nFor a demonstration of a line plot on a polar axis\n\n![image-20250701223807429](01-attention.assets/image-20250701223807429.png)\n\n## Preliminary\n\n### Dot Product Similarity（点积相似度）\n\n给定两个向量 $\\mathbf{q}, \\mathbf{k} \\in \\mathbb{R}^d$\n\n它们的点积为:\n\n$$\n\\text{score} = \\mathbf{q} \\cdot \\mathbf{k} = \\sum_{i=1}^{d} q_i k_i\n$$ {#eq-dot-product}\n\n- 测量两个向量的**相似度**, 数值越大，说明两个向量越相似\n- 在 Self-Attention 中，用来衡量“当前词对其他词的关注程度”\n\n### Softmax 函数\n\n给定向量 $\\mathbf{x} = (x_1, x_2, \\ldots, x_n)$，Softmax 函数定义为:\n$$\n\\text{Softmax}(x_i) = \\frac{e^{x_i}}{\\sum_j e^{x_j}}\n$$ {#eq-softmax}\n\n\n- 将注意力“得分（dot product）”转换为概率分布\n- 每个词对其他词的注意力权重 $\\alpha_{ij} \\in [0, 1]$\n\n![The Transformer Family Version 2.0 | Lil'Log](01-attention.assets/transformer.png)\n\nThis is the figure see, figure @eq-softmax"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-d